;; A major mode for editing AutoHotkey (AHK) script.  Supports commenting,
;; indentation, syntax highlighting, and help lookup both localling and on
;; the web.

;;; INSTALL

;; Open the file, then type “M-x eval-buffer”.  You are done.  Open
